news.title: CapitaLand India Trust to buy one million sq ft IT park in Bengaluru for Rs 1,226 crore
news.para: ​​It will provide funding for the development of the project as part of the forward purchase arrangement, CapitaLand India Trust Management Pte. Ltd, the trustee manager, said in a statement.

news.title: RLDA invites bid for land parcel near Bagdogra station in West Bengal
news.para: ​The proposed land parcel will be leased out for 99 years and the reserve price of the land is Rs 73 crore, an RLDA official said in a statement.

news.title: Berger Paints scouts land in Odisha for new manufacturing plant
news.para: Berger Paints is also gearing up to operationalise the Rs 1,015 crore integrated fully-automated paint manufacturing plant near Lucknow soon.
